net.sf.ntru.polynomial

Class DenseTernaryPolynomial

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.ntru.polynomial.IntegerPolynomial
      • net.sf.ntru.polynomial.DenseTernaryPolynomial
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Polynomial, TernaryPolynomial

    public class DenseTernaryPolynomial
extends IntegerPolynomial
implements TernaryPolynomial
    A TernaryPolynomial with a "high" number of nonzero coefficients.
    Coefficients are represented as an array of length N containing ones, negative ones, and zeros.
